window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Defeat the Bitch Goddess. Rescue my sweetheart. Marry my lovers.</b></p> <p>Lilith, Empress of Demons, has charged me with defeating the Bitch Goddess's remaining generals. My quest will take me beyond the burning sands of the Endless Dunes to the frozen, cursed reaches of the Coldspite Basin.</p> <p>With my lovers by my side–the innocent orcish maiden, the insatiable dragonkin, and the rough and tumble goblin–nothing will get in my way.</p> <p>I will save my sweetheart and destroy the Bitch Goddess before she brings about the end of the world.</p> <p><i>Warning: This novel is not appropriate for all ages; it contains descriptions of violence, unconventional relationships, and limitless adventure.</i></p>"; 
